136
00:15:04,622 --> 00:15:06,249
Ta sẽ xử hắn.

137
00:15:49,458 --> 00:15:50,626
Getsuga...

138
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:54,338
Tenshou!

139
00:16:21,157 --> 00:16:23,367
Chắc chắn hắn vẫn còn thở.

140
